---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Save on Trading Fees - PRUVIQ" description="Save 20% on Binance Futures fees with PRUVIQ's referral. No catch. Lower fees means more profit stays in your pocket.">

  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <p class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-2 tracking-wider">FEES</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-4">
        You're Overpaying<br/>on Every Trade.
      </h1>
      <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-lg mb-8 max-w-2xl">
        Most traders never check their fee structure. Over a year of active trading,
        fees can eat thousands of dollars. Here's how to cut them by 20%.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FEE COMPARISON -->
  <section class="pb-20 border-t border-[--color-border] pt-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Binance Futures Fee Comparison</h2>

      <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg overflow-hidden mb-8">
        <table class="w-full text-sm">
          <thead>
            <tr class="bg-[--color-bg-card]">
              <th class="text-left p-4 font-mono text-[--color-text-muted]">Fee Type</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-mono text-[--color-red]">Standard</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-mono text-[--color-accent]">With PRUVIQ</th>
              <th class="text-center p-4 font-mono text-[--color-accent]">You Save</th>
            </tr>
          </thead>
          <tbody>
            <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border]">
              <td class="p-4">
                <span class="font-bold">Futures Taker</span>
                <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-1">Market orders, stop-loss triggers</p>
              </td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-red]">0.0500%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-accent]">0.0400%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono font-bold text-[--color-accent]">20%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border] bg-[--color-bg-card]">
              <td class="p-4">
                <span class="font-bold">Futures Maker</span>
                <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-1">Limit orders that add liquidity</p>
              </td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-red]">0.0200%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-accent]">0.0160%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono font-bold text-[--color-accent]">20%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border]">
              <td class="p-4">
                <span class="font-bold">Spot Taker</span>
                <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-1">Market orders on spot</p>
              </td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-red]">0.1000%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-accent]">0.0800%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono font-bold text-[--color-accent]">20%</td>
            </tr>
            <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border] bg-[--color-bg-card]">
              <td class="p-4">
                <span class="font-bold">Spot Maker</span>
                <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-1">Limit orders on spot</p>
              </td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-red]">0.1000%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono text-[--color-accent]">0.0800%</td>
              <td class="p-4 text-center font-mono font-bold text-[--color-accent]">20%</td>
            </tr>
          </tbody>
        </table>
      </div>

      <!-- Annual savings calculator -->
      <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] mb-8">
        <h3 class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-sm mb-4">ANNUAL SAVINGS ESTIMATE</h3>
        <div class="overflow-x-auto">
          <table class="w-full text-sm font-mono">
            <thead>
              <tr class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-left">
                <th class="pb-3">Monthly Volume</th>
                <th class="pb-3">Annual Fees (Standard)</th>
                <th class="pb-3">Annual Fees (PRUVIQ)</th>
                <th class="pb-3 text-[--color-accent]">Annual Savings</th>
              </tr>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
              <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border]">
                <td class="py-3">$10,000</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-red]">$120</td>
                <td class="py-3">$96</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-accent]">$24</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border]">
                <td class="py-3">$50,000</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-red]">$600</td>
                <td class="py-3">$480</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-accent]">$120</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border]">
                <td class="py-3">$100,000</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-red]">$1,200</td>
                <td class="py-3">$960</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-accent]">$240</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border]">
                <td class="py-3">$500,000</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-red]">$6,000</td>
                <td class="py-3">$4,800</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-accent]">$1,200</td>
              </tr>
              <tr class="border-t border-[--color-border]">
                <td class="py-3">$1,000,000+</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-red]">$12,000+</td>
                <td class="py-3">$9,600+</td>
                <td class="py-3 text-[--color-accent]">$2,400+</td>
              </tr>
            </tbody>
          </table>
        </div>
        <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-4">
          Based on Binance Futures taker fees (VIP 0 tier). Higher VIP tiers have lower base fees.
          Actual savings depend on your order types and fee tier.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- HOW TO SIGN UP -->
  <section class="pb-20 border-t border-[--color-border] pt-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">How to Get Your Fee Discount</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-lg font-bold shrink-0 w-8">01</div>
          <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Sign Up Through PRUVIQ's Link</h3>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm mb-4">
              Click the button below to create your Binance account with the 20% fee discount automatically applied.
              If you already have a Binance account, you can use the referral code when creating a new Futures account.
            </p>
            <a href="https://www.binance.com/en/futures/ref/PRUVIQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
               class="inline-block bg-[--color-accent] text-[--color-bg] px-6 py-2 rounded font-semibold text-sm hover:bg-[--color-accent-dim] transition-colors">
              Get 20% Fee Discount
            </a>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-3 font-mono">
              Referral Code: PRUVIQ
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-lg font-bold shrink-0 w-8">02</div>
          <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Complete Verification</h3>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
              Binance requires KYC verification for futures trading.
              This takes 5-15 minutes. Your fee discount is applied immediately after verification.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="flex gap-4">
          <div class="font-mono text-[--color-accent] text-lg font-bold shrink-0 w-8">03</div>
          <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card] flex-1">
            <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Trade with Lower Fees</h3>
            <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
              Every futures trade you make will automatically use the discounted fee rate.
              No action needed. The discount is built into your account permanently.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- FAQ -->
  <section class="pb-20 border-t border-[--color-border] pt-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Does PRUVIQ earn from this?</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Yes. When you sign up through our referral link, Binance pays PRUVIQ a commission.
            This commission comes from Binance's revenue, not from your pocket.
            Your fees are always lower than if you signed up without a referral.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">I already have a Binance account. Can I still get the discount?</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            If you haven't opened a Futures account yet, you can still use the referral code when enabling Futures trading.
            If your Futures account is already active, the referral cannot be applied retroactively.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">How long does the fee discount last?</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Binance Futures referral discounts are applied for a period defined by Binance's program terms.
            Check Binance's referral program page for the most current details.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Can I stack this with BNB fee discounts?</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            Yes. Holding BNB and using it for fee deduction gives you an additional 10% discount.
            Combined with the referral discount, your effective fee rate drops even further.
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border border-[--color-border] rounded-lg p-6 bg-[--color-bg-card]">
          <h3 class="font-bold mb-2">Is this financial advice?</h3>
          <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-sm">
            No. PRUVIQ is an educational and research project. We do not provide financial advice.
            Trading cryptocurrency futures involves substantial risk of loss.
            You should carefully consider your financial situation before trading.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section class="pb-20 border-t border-[--color-border] pt-12">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold mb-4">
        Lower Fees = More Profit.
      </h2>
      <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] mb-8 max-w-xl mx-auto">
        It takes 30 seconds to sign up. The discount applies to every trade you make.
      </p>
      <a href="https://www.binance.com/en/futures/ref/PRUVIQ" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
         class="inline-block bg-[--color-accent] text-[--color-bg] px-10 py-4 rounded font-semibold text-lg hover:bg-[--color-accent-dim] transition-colors">
        Get 20% Fee Discount
      </a>
      <p class="text-[--color-text-muted] text-xs mt-6 max-w-lg mx-auto">
        Affiliate disclosure: PRUVIQ earns a commission from Binance when you sign up through our referral link.
        Your trading fee discount is not affected by this commission. Not financial advice.
      </p>
    </div>
  </section>

</Layout>
